# v50 Browser Evaluation — Cursor rule

Source of Truth: `AGENTS.md` `## Browser Evaluation / Scoring Delivery SoT`.

- Browser evaluation must not call Gmail.
- Keep scoring core separated from delivery.
- Preserve legacy ElevenLabs post-call Gmail path unless explicitly changing it.
- Result APIs must not expose raw Claude output, secrets, relay tickets, prompt
  instructions, or raw audio.
- Cloud Tasks payload may include only the normalized evaluation transcript
  required for scoring.
- Use the mock result route before production checks.
- Do not run production Gmail smoke unless explicitly requested.
